              <span id="reviewTextContainer2233826757" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16029276996853216510">My daughter received this book for Christmas and we read it aloud together. A lovely story about hardship, tragedy, yet about love, hard work, savings, with an eventual happy ending. We both enjoyed this one. </span>

