<div id="review_3319012867" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3319012867" />
    <a title="Haley Black" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/109347724-haley-black"><img alt="Haley Black" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1580827616p2/109347724.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3319012867?book_show_action=true">May 04, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Haley Black" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Haley Black" href="/user/show/109347724-haley-black">Haley Black</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/109347724-haley-black?shelf=free-choice-pb">free-choice-pb</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3319012867" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10293500037681851758">This book depicts the story about a young girl and her mother and their dedication to restoring their lives back to normal following a fire that burned all their possessions in their home. I would recommend that children in 1st grade-5th grade read this book because it touches on themes such as family life, saving, hard work, and hardship to an extent. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


