        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2351816119" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10789440639402730524">Text-to Teaching Connection<br/><br/>A Chair For Your Mother by Vera Williams is a great book to teach 3rd-grade Cause and Effect and to discuss need verse wants. It can also utilize as a guided reading book or a read aloud. You can also integrate Math lessons, where students each get a jar with some coins. Students will then sorts the coins by value. Students will then given a worksheet to show how many ways can you make $1.00 from the coins they have. Then students will be asked to total up all the coin</span>
  <span id="freeText10789440639402730524" style="display:none">Text-to Teaching Connection<br /><br />A Chair For Your Mother by Vera Williams is a great book to teach 3rd-grade Cause and Effect and to discuss need verse wants. It can also utilize as a guided reading book or a read aloud. You can also integrate Math lessons, where students each get a jar with some coins. Students will then sorts the coins by value. Students will then given a worksheet to show how many ways can you make $1.00 from the coins they have. Then students will be asked to total up all the coins in the jar.<br /></span>
